status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
https://python.quantecon.org/geom_series.html
\end_layout

\end_inset


\end_layout

\begin_layout Standard
Technically speaking issuing money is as simple as issuing a command to
 
\begin_inset Quotes eld
\end_inset

create
\begin_inset Quotes erd
\end_inset

 a number in a bank's computer system.
 Of course, the commercial bank has to report its daily deposits and lending
 activity to the central bank for oversight and record-keeping.
 Does this then mean that any bank can just print money? Yes and no.
 First, bank licenses are incredibly hard to obtain and banks that have
